        {
            "title": "6月一手撻訂19宗按月減36%  殺訂逾7,700萬反增1.5倍｜連方II等三盤佔最多",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據28Hse內部統計，今年6月全港新盤共有19宗終止買賣合約（撻訂），較5月的30宗減少11宗，按月下跌約36.67%。雖然宗數減少，但涉及金額卻有所上升。按成交紀錄估算，6月遭沒收的訂金總額約7,726.9萬元，較5月的3,022萬元增加約155.66%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個別樓盤方面，撻訂宗數最多的項目依次為連方II有4宗、Grand Seasons有3宗，以及上源有2宗。至於緹外及富豪山峯雖然各只有1宗撻訂，但兩者涉及的沒收訂金金額卻佔據眾新盤首兩位。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2e1a6d17-0598-3458-a97b-fe902c13ad16-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"5月一手撻訂減約36%至30宗 殺訂額降約28%至約3,022萬｜凱柏峰I佔9宗最多\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:5月一手撻訂減約36%至30宗 殺訂額降約28%至約3,022萬｜凱柏峰I佔9宗最多;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3QvkGDy\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">5月一手撻訂減約36%至30宗 殺訂額降約28%至約3,022萬｜凱柏峰I佔9宗最多</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"4月新盤撻訂增逾5成至47宗 殺訂增近倍至近4200萬｜Blue Coast、柏蔚森I同錄9宗居首\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:4月新盤撻訂增逾5成至47宗 殺訂增近倍至近4200萬｜Blue Coast、柏蔚森I同錄9宗居首;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4dIIM6v\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">4月新盤撻訂增逾5成至47宗 殺訂增近倍至近4200萬｜Blue Coast、柏蔚森I同錄9宗居首</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>連方II：4宗撻訂 佔全月宗數約兩成一</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據成交紀錄冊，連方II於6月共有4宗撻訂，佔全月總宗數約21.05%。這4宗撻訂合共涉及沒收訂金約244.81萬元，佔全月一手市場沒收總額約7,726.9萬元的3.17%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述4宗撻訂的買家均已支付樓價一成作訂金。當中涉及沒收金額最高的單位為17樓S10室，原成交價676.3萬元，沒收訂金約67.63萬元；其次為7樓N10室，原成交價613.7萬元，沒收訂金約61.37萬元。其餘兩宗為17及16樓的S7室，原成交價分別為580.5萬與577.6萬元，沒收訂金各約58.05萬及57.76萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇連方II價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇連方II價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4ltaExK\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇連方II價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Grand Seasons：3宗撻訂 佔全月宗數逾一成半</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另一新盤Grand Seasons於6月共有3宗撻訂，佔全月總宗數約15.78%。這3宗撻訂合共涉及沒收訂金約89.36萬元，佔全月一手市場沒收總額約1.16%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>買家均付半成訂金 最大宗沒收近33萬</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述3宗撻訂的買家均已支付樓價半成作訂金。當中沒收金額最高的單位為第1座(1A)的28樓A室，原成交價657.9萬元，沒收訂金約32.89萬元。其餘兩宗分別為第1座(1B)的15樓C室及第1座(1A)的10樓G室，原成交價為654.5萬及474.9萬元，各沒收訂金約32.72萬及23.74萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇Grand Seasons價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇Grand Seasons價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4qS7aXQ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇Grand Seasons價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>上源：2宗撻訂 沒收訂金逾492萬</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上源於6月共有2宗撻訂，合共涉及沒收訂金約492.76萬元，佔全月總額約6.38%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該兩宗撻訂分別位於第1A座G樓A室及第1B座6樓E室，原成交價分別為3,144萬及1,783.6萬元。按沒收金額推算，兩名買家均已支付樓價一成作訂金，撻訂後分別遭沒收約314.4萬及178.36萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇上源放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇上源放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4v4H2df\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇上源放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>緹外及富豪山峯：各佔1宗大額撻訂</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其餘撻訂分布較為分散，其中緹外及富豪山峯各有1宗，合共佔全月總宗數約10.52%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>緹外：沒收訂金達5,400萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">緹外的撻訂為第6座G樓A室，原成交價1.8億元。買家支付三成訂金後取消交易，遭沒收約5,400萬元，佔全月沒收訂金總額約69.89%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇緹外價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇緹外價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4podEfM\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇緹外價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>富豪山峯：沒收訂金逾800萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">富豪山峯的撻訂為第7座6樓A室，原成交價3,818.75萬元。買家支付樓價兩成一作訂金後終止交易，遭沒收約801.93萬元，佔全月沒收訂金總額約10.38%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇富豪山峯放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇富豪山峯放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4w0qXGR\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇富豪山峯放盤】</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tYf3kJQXGfX_v6.ut2GY5w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/2f079f25e5ba7174ea9a83055b78c1cf\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>圖一：2026年6月新盤撻訂記錄</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"緹外\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:緹外;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/緹外\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">緹外</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Blue Coast\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:Blue Coast;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/blue-coast\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Blue Coast</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Grand Seasons\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:Grand Seasons;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/grand-seasons\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Grand Seasons</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"柏蔚森\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:柏蔚森;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/柏蔚森-29007\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">柏蔚森</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"連方\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:連方;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/連方-28093\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">連方</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/6%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%80%E6%89%8B%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%8219%E5%AE%97%E6%8C%89%E6%9C%88%E6%B8%9B36-%E6%AE%BA%E8%A8%82%E9%80%BE7-700%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%8D%E5%A2%9E1-5%E5%80%8D-%E9%80%A3%E6%96%B9II%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%89%E7%9B%A4%E4%BD%94%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A-76659\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
